            "title": "盤中速報 - 大眾控(3701)大漲7.14%，報72元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大眾控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3701:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3701\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3701-TW</a>)21日13:05股價上漲4.8元，報72.0元，漲幅7.14%，成交17,453張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大眾控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3701:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3701\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3701-TW</a>)所屬產業為電腦及週邊設備業，主要業務為H201010一般投資業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲17.89%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.23%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+4,024 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+3,983 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-82 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+123 張</li> <li>融資增減：+2,567 張</li> <li>融券增減：+85 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
